title: John Denver - Christmas Celebration Concert
description:
Source: CD imported into iTunes then exported as MP3's since CD was damaged and unable to be ripped as error free 320cbr. This is 192k/bps and plays mighty fine. - Big Papi

Not many available reviews for this exact CD so suffice it to say this is John Denver and it's country Christmas music. The man is a legend and died in 1997 in his own plane which was an experimental home-made kind. Anyway, good Christmas music for your collection. There's a kid's choir that joins him at one point and they are horrible at first but get better and finish up just fine. - Big Papi
